The paper deals with repairing inconsistent databases, which is a topic in the field of databases (cs.DB). It also involves prioritization and optimization, which are common themes in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of priority relations and the investigation of different lifting semantics suggest a connection to logic (cs.LO). The complexity analysis and algorithm design involve concepts from computational complexity (cs.CC) and data structures (cs.DS).
